lead_paragraph: Spanish police arrested 34 people with alleged links to a tennis match-fixing ring suspected of manipulating bets in tournaments across Spain and Portugal, the Interior Ministry said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Spanish Police Make Arrests in Tennis Match-Fixing Probe
